# Claude global config — commit ONLY the portable, domain-neutral system.
# Everything else (credentials, project data, caches) stays local.

# 1) ignore everything at root by default
/*

# 2) whitelist the portable system files
!/CLAUDE.md
!/commands.md
!/workflow.md
!/settings.json
!/README.md
!/.gitignore

# 3) families/ is tracked but SHIPS EMPTY:
#    generate per-family agents locally with `agents family init`.
!/families/
/families/*
!/families/.gitkeep
